6. API Endpoint Contract
The Agent must generate the following Express.js REST routes:

Auth: POST /api/auth/login

Global Settings:

GET /api/settings (Public)

PUT /api/settings (Protected)

Experiences:

GET /api/experiences (Public, ordered by sortOrder)

POST /api/experiences, PUT /api/experiences/:id, DELETE /api/experiences/:id (Protected)

Projects:

GET /api/projects (Public, ordered by sortOrder)

POST /api/projects, PUT /api/projects/:id, DELETE /api/projects/:id (Protected)

Startups:

GET /api/startups (Public)

POST /api/startups, PUT /api/startups/:id, DELETE /api/startups/:id (Protected)

Contact:

POST /api/contact (Public, Rate-limited)

GET /api/contact/messages (Protected)